{"tid":1013363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港航大派花紅2.5至3個月　3千員工受惠","createTime":"2019-02-08T09:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T10:28:52.000Z","uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7984e8eefb81f5680ff541e44259602d9e27e83","tid":1013363,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"香港航空傳喜訊！香港航空發言人證實，港航本月已向員工派發2個月花紅，今天再出通知，因2016 年業績表現理想，董事會通過，2月會再派多0.5至1個月糧作特別花紅，受惠員工包括空中服務人員、機師、地勤及後勤人員約3,000人。<br />\n<br />\n港航去年新增了11條新航綫，而客運量按年增加約80萬，達660萬人次。發言人指出，今年港航將會繼續新增航線，包括今年6月30日起，正式開通每日一班往來香港至溫哥華國際機場的直航服務，而部分現有航線亦會加密。<br />\n<br />\n近年航空界競爭激烈，國泰航空去年底宣布，所有員工獲發1個月花紅，非管理職級駐港員工明年獲加薪2%，惟較高級員工則需凍薪，加幅是4年來最低、亦低於工會要求的5%，國泰工會表示無奈接受。"},{"pid":"c4721eb434fb894b5a98570265979c4e4f4ddbbb","tid":1013363,"uid":84673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"上年新聞"},{"pid":"a00f572474289112e41ed9e9cf3f99a037cd343c","tid":1013363,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"正 2016"},{"pid":"a8d8379ad5149229d209c64251d8acdb0170e2fa","tid":1013363,"uid":84673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4721eb434fb894b5a98570265979c4e4f4ddbbb","tid":1013363,"uid":84673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"上年新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"前年先岩"},{"pid":"35b31c50f775b5dd5b43115c03bc85f17402c573","tid":1013363,"uid":156375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"兩年前old news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1617b8643ad45ac407ecff03317bc2e8afcbe5d","tid":1013363,"uid":21602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:03:51.000Z","msg":"今年要賣飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03080215e0c632378a5c5dc181646c9e6d6d46a","tid":1013363,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"收到風今年至少都有1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}